description: Need a mid morning snack? Condensed milk should be a cupboard staple, because with only a handful of ingredients and an hour, you can have a delicious cake.
keywords: Cake,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Condensed Milk Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 160 degrees Celsius (my oven is fan forced), grease and lightly flour cake tin.
In a bowl, combine all ingredients and beat on medium speed using electric beaters until the mixture has combined and slightly changed in colour.
Pour batter into pre-prepared tin and bake for 30-45 minutes or until a skewer comes out clean. Time variation depends on pan style - round vs baba
Allow the cake to cool for 10 minutes before turning on to a wire wrack to cool completely.
